About
/$
$
/$
$
The Genesis Center is over 20,000 sq ft,
outreach building completed in 2015.
Seats 800 comfortably for theatre seating and over 500 with round tables for dinners.
The main room has state of the art sound equipment and lighting. The kitchen, which is available, would be any chef's dream.
We will be hosting Sports Ministries featuring pickleball, basketball, volleyball and indoor soccer.
Fine Arts committee is looking forward to concerts and theatre camps. The Genesis Center is also a perfect venue for wedding receptions or business banquets.
The front entry is laid out in brick pavers and your guests will enjoy getting some fresh air while being covered from any possible weather. The entry leads into the Welcoming Room which is spacious and could be ideal for a smaller group setting, for example, birthday or anniversary celebrations.
The Genesis Center is the ultimate location for any event you may be planning. Pictures coming soon. Please do not hesitate to arrange for a walk through to see how we can help you.
